Responsibilities : 
Deliver API schemas that are easy to understand and use. 
Produce API design and technical implementation documents for innovative applications that will ultimately change the way the banking industry operates. 
Remove residual risk from API by delivering reliable robust, resilient and secure software solutions meeting strict operational specifications on a timely basis 
Define application data and resource models such that the operations and relationships between resources are easily understood. 
Exhibit critical thinking to design solutions to solve complex business requirements via existing or new APIs 
Ensure all APIs adhere to the latest API standards to drive design consistency 
Support API developers with delivering highly performant, quality APIs 
Work with Product Managers to find creative ways to increase API usage and engagement. 
Understand and translate the business vision into API(s) and its functions 
Knowledge required 
Design and architecture of APIs and Microservices best practices 
Experience applying modern REST constructs while designing API interface design 
Technical expert in system integrations and data mapping 
RAML schema and API design 
GitHub 
Experience in Spring Boot, Spring Integration and MuleSoft 
Agile and scrum methodology 
Resource modelling 
